  "texts": [
    "LLMs show emergent skill and can perform virtually any textual task and provide glimmers, or \"sparks\", of artificial general intelligence (Microsoft Research, 2023), in the form of a general problem solver as envisioned by Newell and Simon (1972) in the early days of AI research.",
    "Imagine a tool that understands and can complete virtually any task.",
    "Clearly, these LLMs are incredibly useful, and the ease-of-use is quite democratizing.",
    "Yet it remains the case that computational thinking is a set of competences that are unequally distributed through the population (Doleck et al., 2017b).",
    "Findings on computational thinking suggest that those with the requisite competencies have a significant competitive advantage."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "LLMs show emergent skill and can perform virtually any textual task and provide glimmers, or \"sparks\", of artificial general intelligence (Microsoft Research, 2023), in the form of a general problem solver as envisioned by Newell and Simon (1972) in the early days of AI research.",
    "Yet it remains the case that computational thinking is a set of competences that are unequally distributed through the population (Doleck et al., 2017b)."
